assets.description:
Part 4 of 6
Now it's mad, do something fast!

Part 5: https://vr.google.com/objects/8rAX_Jde7Nv?e=VrZandriaUiM1

When making this part, I actually had no clue what the fighter was going to do to survive. I modeled the troll spinning around to charge and realised that the fighter's sword was still stuck in it. At that point my eyes fell on the torch that I had modeled a few frames back and had the idea.
I also like that the fighter had the presence of mind to take a goblin's axe.
